Date and place of birth

05/07/1911 in Montboudif (Cantal, France)

Date and place of death

02/04/1974 in Paris (France)

Nationality

French

Offices held

Director-General of the Rothschild Bank (1956–1962)

Head of General de Gaulle’s Cabinet (1958–1959)

Member of the French National Assembly (1968–1969)

Member of the Constitutional Council (1959–1962)

Prime Minister (1962–1968)

French President (1969–1974)
